ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of NATHALIE THÉBERGE of Gatineau, Quebec, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, and her desgination as Vice-Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of five years, effective April 3, 2024.
